quran[31{c,v,t}:
77,20,kiya hum ne tum ko haqeer pani se nahi pedakiya ?
77,21,is ko aik mehfooz jagah mein rakha
77,22,aik waqt Moueen taq
77,23,phir andaza muqarrarkiya aur humkiya hi khoob andaza muqarrar karne walay hain
77,24,is din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hai
77,25,kiya hum ne zameen ko semathnay wali nahi banaya
77,26,yani ) zndon aur mardon ko
77,27,( banaya ) aur is par ounchay ounchay pahar rakh diye aur tum logon ko meetha pani pilaya
77,28,is din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hai
77,29,jis cheez ko tum jhatlaya karte they. ( ab ) is ki taraf chalo
77,30,( yani ) is saaye ki taraf chalo jis ki teen shaakhen hain
77,31,nah thandhi chaon aur nah lapat se bachao
77,32,is se ( aag ki itni itni barri ) chingariyan urti hain jaisay mehal
77,33,goya zard rang ke oont hain
77,34,is din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hai
77,35,yeh woh din hai ke ( log ) lab taq nah hila saken ge
77,36,aur nah un ko ijazat di jaye gi ke izr kar saken
77,37,is din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hai
77,38,yahi faislay ka din hai ( jis mein ) hum ne tum ko aur pehlay logon ko jamakiya hai
77,39,agar tum ko koi daon aata ho to mujh se kar lau
77,40,is din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hai
77,41,be shak parhaizgaar saayon aur chashmon mein hon ge
77,42,aur meoo mein jo un ko Marghoob hon
77,43,aur jo amal tum karte rahay they un ke badlay mein mazay se khao aur piyo
77,44,hum naiko karon ko aisa hi badla diya karte hain
77,45,is din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hogi
77,46,( ae jhutlanay walo! ) tum kisi qader kha lau aur faiday uttha lau tum be shak gunehgaar ho
77,47,is din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hai
77,48,aur jab un se kaha jata hai ke ( khuda ke agay ) jhuko to jhukatey nahi
77,49,is din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hai
77,50,ab is ke baad yeh kon si baat par imaan layein ge ?
